for%20Pilates.%20They%20began%20asking%20each%20morning%20if%20I%20had%20something%20to%20do%2C%20just%20so%20he%20could%20be%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20experience%2C%20I%20saw%20asking%20for%20help%20as%20a%20burden.%20I%20thought%20our%20family%20would%20be%20upset%20with%20us%20if%20we%20ever%20needed%20them%20to%20watch%20our%20son%2C%20because%20it%20would%20leave%20them%20unable%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20needed%20during%20that%20time.%20I%20also%20felt%20guilty%20for%20leaving%20him.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20seeing%20that%20not%20only%20does%20it%20help%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-near-kids-grandparents-parenting-support-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eform%20bonds%20with%20his%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20also%20brings%20them%20immense%20joy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20and%20grandfather%20outside%20in%20a%20park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690380b50be9845f2dc564cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20son%20and%20grandfather%20often%20play%20together%20outside.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Autumn%20Gavora%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bae0881-b264-4968-b416-d6dc1b753ae3%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20other%20unexpected%20perks%20to%20our%20living%20arrangement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20laughable%20pro%20that%20I%20am%20certainly%20going%20to%20miss%20is%20having%20our%20laundry%20folded.%20My%20husband's%20grandmother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaundry-parents-house-excuse-spend-more-time-together-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloves%20doing%20laundry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20chore%20I%20absolutely%20despise.%20If%20she%20hears%20the%20dryer%20running%2C%20she%20puts%20a%20timer%20on%20her%20phone%20so%20she%20