orth%20American%20business.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaires-boutique-bankruptcy-again-stores-closing-history-2025-8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaire's%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20tween%20staple%20when%20I%20was%20younger.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20jewelry%20and%20trinket%20retailer%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20in%20August.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20to%20Claire's%20to%20see%20how%20the%20'90s%20mall%20icon%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20machines%20haven't%20been%20invented%20yet%2C%20but%20stepping%20into%20my%20local%20Claire's%20felt%20like%20going%20back%20to%20my%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20Claire's%20was%20a%20staple%20for%20affordable%20jewelry%20and%20flavored%20lip%20balms.%20However%2C%20today's%20teens%20and%20tweens%20seem%20to%20be%20obsessed%20with%20beauty%20and%20skincare%20brands%20found%20at%20retailers%20like%20Sephora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20a%20Downtown%20Brooklyn%20Claire's%20was%20running%20a%20%26quot%3BBuy%203%2C%20Get%202%20Free%26quot%3B%20sale%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20check%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20tween%20jewelry%20retailer%20has%20struggled%20to%20find%20its%20footing%20amid%20dying%20mall%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaires-bankrupt-stores-closing-photos-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efiled%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20protection%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20seven%20years%2C%20citing%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20trend%20away%20from%20brick%20and%20mortar%26quot%3B%20and%20higher%20interest%20rates.%20It%20has%20since%20agreed%20to%20sell%20its%20North%20American%20business%2C%20including%20at%20least%20795%20stores%2C%20to%20private%20equity%20firm%20Ames%20Watson%20in%20a%20deal%20worth%20%24140%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retailer%20also%20planned%20to%20close%20about%20290%20US%20stores%2C%20including%20Claire's%20and%20Icing%20locations%2C%20according%20to%20an%20August%2025%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaire's%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20a%20vibe%20check%20at%20Claire's%20amid%20the%20bankruptcy%20proceedings%20and%20sale.%20It%20still%20seems%20to%20be%20going%20for%20the%20teens%2C%20tweens%2C%20and%20children%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20so%20sure%20they're%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20greeted%20by%20a%20Claire's%20staple%20with%20a%20new%20twist.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire's%20piercing%20station%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903b6d4599d46a4ccc12b89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20piercing%20chair%20is%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20for%20many%20tweens.%20Seeing%20the%20hot%20pink%20chair%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20setup%20brought%20back%20my%20own%20Claire's%20memory%20of%20a%20piercing%20gun%20giving%20me%20a%20second%20earring%20hole%20in%20high%20school.%20I%20had%20to%20have%20a%20parent%20with%20me%20since%20I%20was%20only%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20were%20a%20few%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20them%20women%20who%20looked%20over%2018%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20store%20while%20I%20was%20there%2C%20no%20one%20occupied%20the%20sacred%20chair.%20Granted%2C%20it%20was%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day%20on%20Thursday%2C%20so%20the%20tweens%20and%20teens%20who%20are%20Claire's%20target%20demographic%20were%20likely%20all%20in%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20did%2C%20however%2C%20their%20experience%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20limited%20to%20ear%20piercings.%20There%20was%20a%20sign%20advertising%20that%20Claire's%20also%20offers%20nose%20piercings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChildren's%20costumes%20were%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20store.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire's%20costume%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904cae3599d46a4ccc139c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20a%20few%20racks%20of%20fairy%2C%20unicorn%2C%20and%20witchy%20costumes%20in%20time%20for%20Halloween%20season.%20The%20pink%20tutus%20and%20capes%20were%20child-sized%2C%20so%20I%20skipped%20over%20looking%20through%20them%20for%20a%20last-minute%20costume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20reminded%20me%20that%20Claire's%20is%20more%20than%20a%20store%20for%20high%20schoolers%2C%20like%20it%20mainly%20was%20when%20I%20got%20my%20ears%20pierced.%20It's%20also%20a%20place%20for%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20or%20parents%20who%20are%20feeling%20nostalgic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20found%20earrings%20that%20look%20like%20a%20dupe%20for%20a%20luxury%20jewelry%20brand.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20earrings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904cd53c007ca8c27380251%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3B%20Van%20Cleef%20%26amp%3B%20Arpels%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20scanned%20the%20sea%20of%20purple-packaged%20Claire's-branded%20earrings%2C%20one%20burgundy%20and%20gold%20pair%20caught%20my%20attention.%20The%20pair%20I%20picked%20up%20immediately%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20luxury%20jewelry%20brand%20Van%20Cleef%20%26amp%3B%20Arpels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaire's%20earrings%20aren't%20made%20from%20yellow%20gold%2C%20carnelian%2C%20or%20tiger%