hutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20that%20Desiree%20and%20her%20colleagues%20would%20receive%20no%20paycheck%20came%20abruptly.%20Her%20prorated%20check%20for%20the%20last%20days%20worked%20in%20September%20only%20covered%20around%20a%20third%20of%20rent%20at%20the%20apartment%20she%20moved%20into%20over%20the%20summer.%20Like%20other%20DoDEA%20employees%20who%20live%20off%20the%20base%2C%20she's%20also%20stopped%20receiving%20her%20rent%20stipend.%20That%20means%20she'll%20likely%20be%20late%20on%20her%20first%20rent%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20is%20just%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20flowing%2C%20except%20for%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20situations%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20choice.%20It%20has%20to%20keep%20going.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20have%20to%20buy%20food.%20I%20have%20to%20put%20gas%20in%20my%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesiree%20said%20that%20many%20teachers%20may%20have%20just%20incurred%20moving%20costs%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20school%20year%2C%20and%20might%20not%20be%20on%20as%20firm%20a%20financial%20footing.%20One%20fairly%20new%20DoDEA%20employee%20said%20that's%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20weak%20dollar%20compared%20to%20the%20euro.%20It's%20made%20it%20even%20harder%20to%20save%20up%20ahead%20of%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20bank%20account's%20already%20in%20the%20negative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%20personally%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20make%20rent%20next%20month.%20I%20don't%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20strain%20is%20that%20some%20overseas%20DoDEA%20workers%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20pick%20up%20second%20jobs%2C%20a%20backup%20plan%20helping%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firs-lawyer-shysters-hot-dog-stand-isaac-stein-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS-based%20federal%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20stay%20afloat.%20Living%20across%20the%20ocean%20from%20loved%20ones%20adds%20to%20the%20stress%2C%20making%20things%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20tougher%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Indresano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20being%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20being%20able%20to%20go%20to%20a%20food%20bank%20that%20they%20would%20have%20there%20%E2%80%94%20not%20that%20we%20need%20that%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20but%20you%20never%20know.%20It%20depends%20on%20how%20long%20this%20lasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Indresano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b3ed3bf-9af2-4034-98c7-5637dfb2d805%5C%22%3EThe%20government%20shutdown%20hits%20classrooms%20overseas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20and%20students%20on%20overseas%20military%20bases%20recently%20fought%20to%20keep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fshutdown-cancels-sports-games-dances-students-military-base-schools-rcna235545%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextracurriculars%20and%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%20running%20amid%20a%20funding%20lapse%2C%20but%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20of%20teaching%2C%20the%20shutdown%20still%20looms.%20One%20teacher%20pointed%20to%20the%20classroom%20snacks%20they%20and%20their%20colleagues%20often%20pay%20for%20out%20of%20their%20own%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20families%20that%20don't%20have%20the%20food%20and%20things%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20teacher%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20teachers%20are%20providing%20snacks.%20We%20can't%20go%20buy%20that%20for%20them%20because%20we're%20not%20getting%20paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesiree%20said%20she's%20been%20unable%20to%20buy%20school%20supplies%2C%20something%20the%20school%20usually%20gets%20an%20allowance%20for.%20That%20means%20that%20their%20ceramics%20classes%20could%20go%20without%20clay%2C%20and%20the%20school%20could%20run%20out%20of%20paper%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20has%20been%20teaching%20overseas%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20He's%20weathered%20multiple%20shutdowns%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20his%20paycheck%20has%20been%20suspended.%20Having%20spent%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20time%20in%20his%20local%20community%2C%20he%20sees%20familiar%20faces%20at%20the%20coffee%20shop%20and%20grocery%20store.%20Some%20of%20the%20locals%20have%20heard%20about%20the%20shutdown%2C%20or%20they%20ask%20what's%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20surprise%20as%20well%20as%20sympathy%20for%20what%20we're%20going%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20However%2C%20he's%20observed%20that%20his%20local%20friends%20struggle%20to%20%26quot%3Bwrap%20their%20mind%20around%20how%20Congress%2C%20meaning%20both%20the%20House%20and%20the%20Senate%2C%26quot%3B%20could%20let%20the%20government%20shut%20down%20and%20workers%20go%20without%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20conceptualize%20how%20that%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-military-teachers-pay-overseas-unpaid-rent-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762079102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904ebacc007ca8c27380740%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-military-teachers-pay-overseas-unpaid-rent-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teachers%20on%20military%20bases%20across%20the%20pond%20are%20working%20without%20pay%20amid%20the%20shutdown%2C%20Their%20landlords%20are%20confused%20why%20they%20suddenly%20can't%20pay%20rent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jkaplan%40businessinsider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-military-teachers-pay-overseas-unpaid-rent-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20%26quo