20delightful%20behind-the-scenes%20story.%20When%20the%20crew%20suggested%20serving%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20luxurious%20chicken%20for%20his%20scenes%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20go%20for%20traditional%20homemade%20mutton%20instead.%20Dholakia%20noted%20that%20this%20decision%20aligned%20perfectly%20with%20his%20character's%20authenticity%2C%20bringing%20a%20genuine%20and%20captivating%20energy%20to%20the%20film%20that%20audiences%20wouldn't%20soon%20forget.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20quit%20our%20jobs%20and%20turned%20our%20obsession%20with%20true%20crime%20into%20a%20hit%20podcast%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20then%20we%20broke%20news%20on%20a%20major%20murder%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%CC%81ine%20Cain%20and%20Kevin%20Greenlee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690699ac599d46a4ccc14d17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EA%CC%81ine%20Cain%20and%20Kevin%20Greenlee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20a%20married%20couple%20who%20channeled%20our%20mutual%20obsession%20with%20true%20crime%20into%20a%20full-time%20podcasting%20business%20that%20eventually%20replaced%20our%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20gave%20four%20years%20of%20our%20lives%20to%20one%20particularly%20haunting%20murder%20case%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Delphi%20murders%20%E2%80%94%20producing%20hundreds%20of%20podcast%20episodes%2C%20breaking%20news%2C%20and%20ultimately%20writing%20and%20publishing%20a%20crime%20nonfiction%20book%20about%20the%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20got%20pretty%20wild.%20We%20endured%20extreme%20conditions%20at%20a%20month-long%20murder%20trial%2C%20sitting%20out%20in%20the%20cold%2C%20going%20without%20food%20or%20water%2C%20and%20skipping%20sleep%20in%20order%20to%20get