ng%2C%20occasionally%20absurd%2C%20and%20always%20meticulous.%20They%20sprint%2C%20squat%2C%20and%20dance.%20If%20their%20movements%20are%20deemed%20not%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20worker%20said%2C%20their%20performance%20is%20critiqued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20one%20of%20many%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20Figure%20and%201X%2C%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20complex%20human%20behavior%20in%20a%20robot.%20The%20ultimate%20goal%2C%20as%20with%20much%20of%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20might%20be%20autonomy%2C%20but%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earmy%20of%20flesh-and-blood%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20props%20up%20the%20sleek%20demos%20and%20lofty%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295252ac5-4747-45bd-8842-1bf4f8f8f9fd%5C%22%3E'Teaching%20a%20baby'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraining%20a%20robot%20to%20be%20human%20isn't%20glamorous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20data%20collectors%20start%20out%20wiping%20down%20a%20table%2C%20sometimes%20for%20weeks.%20%26quot%3BYou%20take%20a%20step%2C%20wipe%20the%20table%2C%20go%20into%20a%20reset%20pose%2C%20and%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20said.%20It's%20%26quot%3Brinse%20and%20repeat%20until%20break%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20receive%20detailed%20documents%20about%20how%20to%20perform%20simple%20tasks%2C%20and%20they're%20guided%20by%20a%20thick%2C%20constantly%20evolving%20manual%2C%20three%20workers%20said.%20They're%20also%20paired%20up%20with%20a%20peer%20to%20ensure%20the%20tasks%20are%20performed%20correctly%2C%20five%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20is%20very%20strict%20on%20how%20everything%20needs%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20very%20tough%20mentally%20and%20physically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20data%20collection%20started%2C%20workers%20have%20largely%20used%20motion%20capture%20suits%20to%20teleoperate%20the%20robot%20%E2%80%94%20teaching%20it%20with%20manual%20movement.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20company%20told%20workers%20it%20was%20pivoting%20away%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-musk-optimus-humanoid-robot-training-motion-capture-cameras-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emotion-capture%20suits%20and%20teleoperation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20toward%20collecting%20data%20using%20only%20cameras%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20The%20change%20followed%20the%20departure%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-org-chart-executives-elon-musk-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogram%20director%20Milan%20Kovac.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker-mounted%20cameras%20point%20in%20all%20directions%2C%20helping%20precisely%20place%20the%20data%20collectors%20in%20the%20environment%2C%20workers%20said.%20They%20said%20the%20team%20was%20told%20it%20would%20be%20faster%20to%20scale%20data%20collection%20without%20the%20motion-capture%20suits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20June%20shift%2C%20the%20company%20has%20incorporated%20multiple%20new%20training%20processes%2C%20including%20stationing%20cameras%20around%20workers%20while%20they%20perform%20tasks%2C%20three%20workers%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Aitken%2C%20a%20robotics%20expert%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Sheffield%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20camera%20towers%20could%20supplement%20the%20data%20by%20providing%20a%20broader%20view%20of%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221010%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla's%20Optimus%20Robot%20is%20pictured%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffaae30be9845f2dc52903%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221051%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Optimus%20robot%20handed%20out%20candy%20in%20Times%20Square.%3Cp%3EWill%20Coggins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20are%20sometimes%20outfitted%20with%20haptic%20gloves%2C%20which%20track%20the%20minute%20movements%20of%20their%20hands%2C%20three%20employees%20said.%20Musk%20has%20said%20Tesla%20has%20spent%20considerable%20energy%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20human-like%20hand%20for%20Optimus%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20incredibly%20difficult%20engineering%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20have%20also%20recorded%20themselves%20mirroring%20each%20other's%20movements%2C%20three%20people%20said.%20At%20the%20company's%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20plant%2C%20data%20collectors%20have%20organized%20vehicle%20parts%20and%20worked%20on%20conveyor%20belts%20while%20wearing%20the%20headset%20and%20backpack%2C%20two%20people%20said.%20Experts%20who%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20said%20that%20collecting%20different%20data%20points%20for%20the%20same%20task%20can%20be%20helpful%20for%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tasks%20are%20so%20simple%20that%20a%20former%20worker%20likened%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bteaching%20a%20baby.%26quot%3B%20Two%20data%20collectors%20said%20they%20recorded%20themselves%20working%20on%20brain%20teasers%20designed%20for%20actual%20babies%3A%20putting%20rings%20on%20by%20size%20and%20color%2C%20or%20putting%20shapes%20into%20their%20corresponding%20slots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20also%20begun%20using%20AI-generated%20prompts%20to%20help%20train%20the%20robot%2C%20three%20people%20said.%20During%20some%20training%20exercises%2C%20workers%20receive%20a%20series%20of%20AI-generated%20prompts%20via%20a%20headset%2C%20which%20is%20attached%20to%20the%2030-%20to%2040-pound%20backpack%20via%20wires.%20Though%20they're%20often%20wearing%20the%20backpack%2C%20it%20sometimes%20sits%20nearby%20on%20a%20chair%20or%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20said%20the%20exercises%20have%20included%20squatting%2C%20doing%20the%20%26quot%3BChicken%20Dance%2C%26quot%3B%20acting%20like%20a%20gorilla%2C%20pretending%20to%20vacuum%2C%20sprinting%20for%20several%20yards%2C%20pretending%20to%20golf%2C%20and%20twerking.%20Workers%20are%20expected%20to%20perform%20each%20exercise%20within%20three%20to%20five%20seconds%2C%20the%20workers%20said.%20Two%20people%20recalled%20instances%20where%20some%20tasks%20made%20them%20uncomfortable%2C%20including%20AI-generated%20requests%20to%20crawl%20on%20all%20fours%20or%20remove%20a%20piece%20of%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAitken%20said%20the%20seemingly%20random%20tasks%20could%20help%20Tesla%20understand%20which%20areas%20it%20needs%20to%20improve%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20know%20you've%20covered%20the%20entire%20range%20of%20things%20you'll%20need%20it%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271e09365-83af-4145-9e28-51310de851ef%5C%22%3E'Cardio%20all%20day'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20can%20take%20a%20physical%20toll%2C%20four%20people%20said.%20One%20former%20worker%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20doing%20cardio%20all%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20worker%20said%20they%20sustained%20a%20back%20injury%20while%20training%20the%20robot.%20They%20said%20the%20unbalanced%20weight%20of%20the%20backpack%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20they%20were%20constantly%20%26quot%3Bwalking%20with%20a%20limp.%26quot%3B%20They%20said%20they%20went%20on%20medical%20leave%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lost%20feeling%20in%20my%20right%20leg%20and%20had%20a%20sharp%20pain%20in%20my%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20said%20they%20saw%20colleagues%20sustain%20back%20and%20neck%20injuries%20due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20experienced%20problems%20during%20teleoperation%2C%20which%20can%20involve%20motion-capture%20suits%20and%20a%20virtual%20reality%20headset.%20A%20mix%20of%20poor%20image%20quality%20and%20the%20length%20of%20time%20workers%20spent%20wearing%20the%20gear%20triggered%20severe%20motion%20sickness%2C%20three%20people%20said.%20They%20said%20it%20could%20be%20especially%20disorienting%20when%20the%20robot%20fell%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20have%20the%20feeling%20you're%20falling%20because%20you're%20seeing%20through%20its%20eyes%2C%20but%20you'd%20be%20standing%20upright%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20teleoperation%20is%20mostly%20reserved%20for%20investor%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investors%20want%20to%20see%20the%20bots%20moving%20in%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we're%20in%20mo-cap%2C%20we're%20controlling%20the%20bots%20so%20it%20looks%20more%20fluid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20sometimes%20accompanied%20by%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20brought%20his%205-year-old%20son%20X%20to%20see%20the%20robot%2C%20two%20former%20workers%20said.%20One%20of%20the%20former%20workers%20compared%20the%20demos%20to%20%26quot%3Bputting%20on%20a%20big%20show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20the%20time%2C%20two%20workers%20said%2C%20the%20robot%20tumbles%20over%20when%20performing%20tasks%20that%20require%20bending%20or%20leaning%2C%20sometimes%20damaging%20expensive%20equipment.%20It's%20typically%20strapped%20into%20the%20gantry%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1922083384085430492%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20supportive%20rig%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20keeps%20the%20robot%20upright%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20it's%20performing%20tasks%20that%20involve%20traveling%20more%20than%20a%20few%20feet%2C%20three%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAitken%20said%20the%20robot%20should%20be%20able%20to%20remain%20upright%20with%20e