0modern%20family%20governance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20man%20who%20taught%20dynasties%20that%20the%20secret%20to%20keeping%20their%20money%20isn't%20about%20spreadsheets%20or%20tax%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20about%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fought%20against%20%5Bthe%20word%20wealth%5D%20because%20I%20didn't%20think%20its%20financial%20definition%20was%20where%20wealth%20actually%20was%20in%20a%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jpmorgan-is-training-employees-artificial-intelligence-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHughes%20told%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3BFamily%20Legacy%26quot%3B%20blog%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20one%20day%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20word%20wealth%20is%20a%20derivation%20of%20well-being.%20I%20just%20didn't%20understand%20the%20breadth%20of%20the%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20I'm%20living%20with%20that%20wonder%20that%20wealth%20means%20well-being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20insight%20reshaped%20an%20entire%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20most%20family%20fortunes%20evaporate%20by%20the%20third%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20phenomenon%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bshirtsleeves%20to%20shirtsleeves%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Hughes%20believes%20the%20problem%20isn't%20poor%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20bad%20family%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a459150-daa3-4e87-a01b-aeaed6dab768%5C%22%3EThe%20five%20capitals%20that%20determine%20a%20family's%20fate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20believes%20that%20families%20who%20focus%20only%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkathleen-grace-family-fortune-generational-wealth-children-money-lessons-advice-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoney%20eventually%20lose%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20of%20bad%20investments%2C%20but%20because%20they%20neglect%20the%20other%20forms%20of%20wealth%20that%20keep%20people%20connected%20and%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20breaks%20down%20true%20wealth%20into%20five%20kinds%20of%20capital%2C%20all%20of%20which%20he%20said%20must%20grow%20together%20if%20a%20family%20hopes%20to%20last%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20a%20family%20exists%20is%20to%20enhance%20the%20lives%20of%20its%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20every%20member%20is%20flourishing%2C%20the%20whole%20system%20is%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20kind%2C%20legacy%20capital%2C%20is%20the%20shared%20purpose%20that%20binds%20the%20family%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sense%20of%20why%20it%20exists%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20capital%20reflects%20the%20family's%20ability%20to%20make%20decisions%20together%20and%20manage%20conflict.%20Intellectual%20capital%20is%20what%20the%20family%20learns%20and%20passes%20down%20%E2%80%94%20the%20knowledge%2C%20traditions%2C%20and%20skills%20that%20compound%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuman%20capital%20represents%20the%20growth%20and%20well-being%20of%20each%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20financial%20capital%20should%20never%20dominate%2C%20Hughes%20said%20%E2%80%94%20its%20role%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20and%20grow%20those%20other%20four%20qualitative%20capitals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20four%20qualitative%20capitals%20that%20determines%20your%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%20%26quot%3BFamilies%20that%20align%20their%20financial%20capital%20in%20service%20to%20growing%20those%20four%20qualitative%20capitals%20become%20families%20of%20affinity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204834b7d-0dd1-42a6-ad87-0c49c5711b05%5C%22%3EFrom%20creators%20of%20wealth%20to%20creators%20of%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20fortunes%20crumble%2C%20Hughes%20believes%2C%20because%20the%20second%20generation%20fails%20to%20redefine%20what%20the%20first%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20generation%20creates%20the%20wealth%20and%20the%20second%20generation%20creates%20the%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20great%20question%20for%20them%20is%2C%20can%20they%20create%20family%3F%20And%20can%20they%20sustain%20the%20dream%20process%20for%20the%20new%20family%20members%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%2C%20in%20his%20view%2C%20depends%20on%20whether%20the%20next%20generation%20feels%20%26quot%3Battracted%26quot%3B%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283b8c224-b09e-472c-a309-0a14120270bd%5C%22%3EThe%20missing%20role%20of%20elders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20also%20warned%20that%20many%20modern%20families%20underestimate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-life-advice-helped-me-start-fresh-from-grandma-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20importance%20of%20elders%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20those%20who%20preserve%20culture%2C%20tell%20stories%2C%20and%20mediate%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomewhat%20sadly%20in%20modernity%2C%20we%20have%20lost%20connection%20with%20the%20roles%20of%20elders%20and%20how%20necessary%20they%20are%20to%20a%20flourishing%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20elders%20nurture%20relationships%20and%20reinforce%20the%20family's%20values%2C%20they%20create%20what%20Hughes%20called%20%26quot%3Baffinity%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20invisible%20glue%20that%20keeps%20future%20generations%20connected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295e6e155-0ae5-4007-a1b6-674d7924ac7c%5C%22%3EA%20shift%20from%20money%20to%20meaning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20half%20a%20century%20of%20advising%20global%20dynasties%2C%20Hughes%20has%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20courage%20%E2%80%94%20not%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20rarest%20form%20of%20family%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20family%20needs%20courage%20to%20really%20imagine%20itself%20100%20