20day%26quot%3B%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20says%20a%20national%20emergency%20lets%20him%20issue%20sweeping%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20no%20other%20president%20has%20done.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20Trump%20could%20still%20pull%20off%20his%20trade%20plans%20without%20them%2C%20but%20it'll%20be%20harder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20declared%20a%20national%20emergency.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bbeen%20looted%2C%20pillaged%2C%20raped%2C%20and%20plundered%26quot%3B%20by%20other%20countries%20through%20trade%20deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImposing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20tariff%20of%20at%20least%2010%25%20on%20nearly%20every%20single%20country%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20address%20the%20problem%2C%20Trump%20said.%20Select%20countries%2C%20like%20Brazil%20and%20India%2C%20would%20be%20subjected%20to%20even%20higher%20tariffs%2C%20which%20are%20taxes%20imposed%20on%20imported%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20hear%20arguments%20over%20whether%20those%20tariffs%20can%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20kicks%20Trump's%20tariffs%20to%20the%20curb%2C%20it'll%20be%20taking%20away%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20and%20flexible%20tools%20the%20president%20has%20used%20to%20pursue%20his%20economic%20agenda.%20If%20it%20lets%20Trump%20keep%20them%2C%20it'll%20reflect%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ever-broadening%20view%20of%20presidential%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20legally%20justify%20the%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20taxes%20on%20American%20importers%2C%20the%20White%20House%20leaned%20on%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%2C%20or%20IEEPA.%20The%20Carter-era%20law%20allows%20presidents%20to%20limit%20international%20transactions%20after%20declaring%20a%20national%20emergency%2C%20and%20has%20typically%20been%20used%20to%20justify%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20considering%20whether%20the%20IEEPA%20allows%20presidents%20to%20impose%20tariffs%2C%20a%20power%20no%20previous%20president%20has%20ever%20claimed.%20If%20the%20court%20decides%20yes%2C%20it'll%20take%20up%20a%20second%20issue%3A%20Whether%20giving%20the%20president%20this%20power%20tramples%20upon%20Article%20I%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20says%20it's%20Congress's%20job%20to%20set%20and%20collect%20taxes%20and%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20questions%20give%20the%20justices%20room%20to%20choose%20their%20own%20adventure%20in%20how%20they%20approach%20the%20case%2C%20according%20to%20Rachel%20Brewster%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20international%20trade%20at%20Duke%20Law%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20text%20of%20the%20IEEPA%2C%20they%20might%20be%20more%20inclined%20to%20uphold%20the%20decisions%20of%20lower%20courts%2C%20which%20found%20the%20tariffs%20illegal%2C%20she%20said.%20If%20their%20questions%20center%20on%20national%20security%2C%20things%20could%20swing%20in%20Trump's%20favor%2C%20according%20to%20Brewster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20multiple%20frames%2C%26quot%3B%20Brewster%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20mix%20of%20all%20these%20things%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20mix%20of%20domestic%20taxation%2C%20it's%20a%20mix%20of%20domestic%20regulation%2C%20but%20it%20also%20implicates%20foreign%20imports%20and%20foreign%20negotiation.%20So%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20wiggle%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f20b774b-8c8b-4fee-b747-5fbb5c9c5116%5C%22%3ENo%20taxation%20without%20justification%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIEEPA%20doesn't%20say%20anything%20about%20letting%20presidents%20invent%20new%20taxes%20or%20tariffs%20in%20response%20to%20national%20emergencies.%20Instead%2C%20the%20law%20allows%20presidents%20to%20%26quot%3Bregulate%26quot%3B%20importation%2C%20which%20the%20Trump%20administration%20says%20covers%20the%20power%20to%20unilaterally%20impose%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20opposing%20the%20IEPPA%20tariffs%20have%20argued%20that%20Congress%20has%20passed%20plenty%20of%20other%20laws%20that%2C%20under%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20allow%20presidents%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20without%20explicit%20congressional%20permission.%20Legislators%20could%20have%20included%20that%20power%20in%20IEEPA%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20liberation%20day%20reciprocal%20tariffs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69050d330be9845f2dc584b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20presented%20a%20poster%20board%20listing%20the%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20he%20imposed%20on%20other%20countries%20on%20%26quot%3Bliberation%20day.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20taken%20the%20unprecedented%20measure%20of%20using%20this%20novel%20power%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20one%20of%20his%20biggest%20economic%20priorities%2C%20said%20Alan%20Wolff%2C%20a%20former%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%2C%20who%20has%20negotiated%20trade%20deals%20in%20both%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20administrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20uncharted%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolff%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNo%20president%20has%20ever%20done%20anything%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decides%2C%20it%20would%20apply%20only%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20announced%20on%20%26quot%3Bliberation%20day%26quot%3B%20and%