0realised%20that%20my%20vision%20of%20coexistence%20is%20coming%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20biosphere%20reserve%20operates%20under%20strict%20rules%3A%20vehicles%20and%20plastic%20are%20not%20allowed.%20The%20only%20exception%20is%20a%20single%20electric%20farm%20utility%20vehicle%2C%20which%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20silent%20safari%20vehicle%2C%20ensuring%20minimal%20disturbance%20to%20the%20animals.%20Visitors%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20bring%20any%20plants%20or%20seeds%20into%20the%20biosphere.%20Every%20effort%20is%20made%20to%20avoid%20activities%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rule%20in%20this%20biosphere%20is%20that%20nature%20comes%20first%2C%20not%20humans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20small%20homes%20on%20the%20property%20for%20overnight%20stays%2C%20built%20without%20cement%20and%20bricks%2C%20using%20prefabricated%20construction%20methods.%20Jai%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20eco-tourism%20spot%20but%20rather%20a%20model%20intended%20to%20inspire%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20rewild%20their%20own%20spaces.%20He%20has%20also%20written%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20motivate%20others%20to%20take%20similar%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20already%20feel%20like%20the%20richest%20person%20on%20the%20planet.%20I%20have%20created%20more%20wealth%20over%20the%20past%202.5%20years%20than%20in%20the%2050%20years%20before%20that.%20One%20must%20realise%20that%20richness%20is%20not%20in%20our%2030%2C000%20sq%20ft%20mansions%20and%20apartments%20in%20cities.%20The%20richness%20lies%20in%20mental%20peace%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20found.%20Most%20days%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20even%20walking%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20