20to%20clock%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20crore%2C%20of%20which%2C%20his%20profit%20margin%20is%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20did%20not%20come%20easy%20to%20Hrushikesh.%20Initially%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20plant%20aloe%20vera%20on%20the%20field%20was%20greatly%20opposed%20by%20his%20in-laws.%20His%20wife%20Madhura%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20newly%20married%20then%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20have%20much%20idea%20about%20the%20crop.%20My%20parents%20were%20against%20this%20decision.%20They%20believed%20aloe%20vera%20could%20bring%20us%20misery%20as%20the%20plant%20has%20thorns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20my%20husband%20proved%20them%20wrong.%20Now%2C%20my%20parents%20often%20take%20aloe%20vera%20from%20our%20field%20to%20apply%20on%20their%20hair%20and%20drink%20its%20juice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20success%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20planting%20aloe%20vera%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20if%20you%20plant%20thorny%20plants%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20bad%20luck.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20a%C2%A0kachha%C2%A0house%2C%20but%20today%2C%20I%20have%20built%20a%20two-storey%20home%20in%20my%20village%20and%20we%20travel%20in%20a%20Fortuner%20car!%20All%20this%20became%20possible%20only%20because%20of%20growing%20aloe%20vera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20farmers%20should%20not%20be%20swayed%20solely%20by%20potential%20earnings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20significant%20profits%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296876%2Frajasthan-tea-seller-earns-lakhs-from-aloe-vera-farming-juice-products%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20likely%20if%20we%20focus%20on%20producing%20products%20and%20expanding%20the%20operation%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757313000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D497045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20drought-prone%20Satara%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20turned%20adversity%20into%20success%20by%20making%20aloe%20vera%20products%20like%20soaps%2C%20shampoos%2C%20and%20juices%2C%20building%20a%20multi-crore%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F497045%2Faloe-vera-farming-success-story-satara-farmer-hrushikesh-dhane-maharashtra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20How%20a%20Snake%20Rescue%20in%20a%20Delhi%20School%20Taught%20a%20Lesson%20in%20Coexistence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F458137%2Fhimachal-monsoon-travel-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeavy%20monsoon%20rains%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20drenched%20South%20Delhi%20when%20panic%20rippled%20through%20a%20school%20campus.%20In%20the%20storeroom%20of%20Kendriya%20Vidyalaya%2C%20NMR%2C%20staff%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20unexpected%20guest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20large%20snake%20coiled%20in%20the%20corner.%20Instead%20of%20fear%20turning%20into%20chaos%2C%20what%20followed%20was%20a%20lesson%20in%20calm%20and%20coexistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20swiftly%2C%20Principal%20Chandan%20Kohli%20called%20Wildlife%20SOS%2C%20the%20non-profit%20known%20for%20rescuing%20and%20rehabilitating%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20the%20rescue%20here%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3